#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="22"></a><a class="wp" id="wp15"></a>
msgctxt "dn6:30.1"
msgid "Ekamidāhaṃ, mahāli, samayaṃ kosambiyaṃ viharāmi ghositārāme."
